1. The farmer picked a crisp red apple.
2. For lunch, I decided to eat a green apple.
3. She took a big bite out of the juicy apple.
4. The teacher rewarded the student with a shiny apple.
5. In the basket, there was only one rotten apple.
6. He rolled the round fruit across the table until it hit the apple.
7. The pie recipe calls for exactly six pounds of apple.
8. Snow White was tempted by the poisoned apple.
9. My favorite snack is a sliced apple.
10. The logo on the computer screen is a bitten apple. [end of text]


